Package br.octahedron.cotopaxi.config

Interface Summary
CotopaxiConfig This entity provides methods to change Cotopaxi's configuration.
CotopaxiConfigurator Indicates that a class is a ModelFacades and can be used by controller.
CotopaxiConfigView A view for all Cotopaxi's configuration parameters.
 

Class Summary
CotopaxiConfigView.Handler Handles and provides access to the unique ControllerConfigView instance.
CotopaxiConfigViewImpl The controller configuration.
